{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"红十月之歌","authors":["孙瑞卿"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红十月之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空军部队　孙瑞卿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的天啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上十九年啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜多少风和雨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今守在哨所迎“十一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限骄傲无限喜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦擦手中的革命枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸身上的绿军衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士笑脸望祖国啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮澎湃热泪滴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的宏图谁描绘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的风雷谁唤起？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的红旗谁高举？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的道路谁开辟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山冲走出巨人来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万峰都显低！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“枪杆子里面出政权”啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的声音震寰宇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的脚步走南北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛委员高举列宁的旗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘江两岸舞红缨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山上燃火炬……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流二万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的炮声猛又密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把三座大山全砸碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堂堂的新中国顶天立！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨中国赫鲁晓夫大叛徒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用“阶级斗争熄灭”论作虎皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑枪毒箭握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向无产阶级阵地搞偷袭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在天安门上挥巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命风雷激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万水兵马动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把资产阶级老巢砸成泥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几度狂风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少暴雨洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级队伍更纯洁更坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义江山更壮丽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看今天，革命形势无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想空前大普及；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜今日全国一片红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席开创人类历史新世纪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊，毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的指示威力无比；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战无不胜的毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导革命创奇迹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦擦手中的革命枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸身上的绿军衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士在哨所迎“十一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对毛主席发誓语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战斗的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱永生永世唱下去；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战斗的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱坚定不移走到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千声万声唱不完啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《东方红》颂歌震天响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千遍万遍喊不够啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福毛主席万寿无疆！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}